flowchart_mermaid:
flowchart TD
  A[Idle interval] --> B{Automation enabled?}
  B -- no --> Z[Stop]
  B -- yes --> B2{Current node is owner or override?}
  B2 -- no --> Z2[Skip without scan/lease/claim]
  B2 -- yes --> C[Scan Kanban automatically]
  C --> D{Item or ancestor automation_excluded?}
  D -- yes --> X[Skip/cancel branch markers]
  D -- no --> E[Review Processor]
  D -- no --> F[Preprocessing Processor]
  E --> G{Review text exists and source changed?}
  G -- no --> H[No review work]
  G -- yes --> I[Queue/process review marker through hermes-kanban-review-processor]
  I --> I2{Failure?}
  I2 -- yes --> I3[Record failure event and next_retry_at]
  I3 --> I4[Retry when due unless superseded/cancelled]
  F --> J{Open ordinary leaf in ToDo lane?}
  J -- no --> K[No preprocessing work]
  J -- yes --> L{Processed marker matches current source?}
  L -- yes --> M[No preprocessing work]
  L -- no --> L2{Exact accepted preprocessing decision proves interrupted finalization?}
  L2 -- yes --> L3[Reconcile existing marker to processed]
  L2 -- no --> N[Queue/process preprocessing marker through hermes-kanban-preprocessor]
  N --> O{Result}
  O -- ready --> P[Persist decision and readiness marker, then complete processor marker]
  O -- decomposition --> Q[Create/confirm children and move parent out of ToDo]
  O -- blocked/question --> R[Create visible blocker/question]
  O -- failure --> S[Record failure event and next_retry_at]
